---
title: Creamy Mushroom and Chicken Breast Lovers' Ravioli with Spinach
description: Mushroom lovers, rejoice! We're doubling down on mushrooms tonight. Mushroom ravioli is tossed with more mushrooms in a creamy white wine sauce, then topped with Parmesan for a luxurious veggie-forward dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220929_R1018_W46_CA_RV155902-1__MB_Main_remove_nuts_low-9883bf07.jpg
